<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="angle-n">angle <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'æŋɡl/    美 /'æŋɡl/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>角：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>at a 90-degree angle to the ground
和地面呈90度角</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a dead angle
死角</p></div>

<h4 id="2-point-of-view">2.★ <strong>角度；观点(point of view)；方面：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Try looking at the affair <strong>from a</strong> different <strong>angle</strong>.
试着从另一个角度来看这件事。</p></div></div>